# Agent Instructions (Template)

## Runtime Modes
- `container-beads`: Beads enabled and required for issue tracking
- `local-lite`: host-only workflows, no direct Beads commands

## Session Start
```bash
make agent-runtime-resolve
make agent-init ISSUE=<id> ACTOR=<agrc/copilot|agrc/roo|agrc/claude>
```

## Core Rules
- Use Beads as system of record.
- Keep milestone comments and structured notes current.
- Run QA gate before closure.
